Message

Hello everyone. This bot is owned by "Atom Production#3656". I am making new more and cool command was comming soon. If you have any suggestions or feedback drop in my DMs "Atom Production". I am waiting for you.

Description

Wyvern is Multi-Talentent bot have cool features and i never stop adding new commands after every month. You can see COMMANDS there you can see command which is added.

Commands

ban Description: ban a member. Usage: hey ban [time] [reason] kick Description: kick a member. Usage: hey kick [reason] warn Description: warn a member. Usage: hey warn mute Description: mute a member. Usage: hey mute [time] [reason] unmute Description: unmute a member. Usage: hey unmute clear Description: clear messages. Usage: hey clear autorole Description: set role to be given to member on join. Usage: hey autorole log Description: set channel to log to. Usage: hey log ping Description: check the bots ping. Usage: hey ping warns Description: see the members warnings. Usage: hey warns [user] config Description: view this servers config Usage: hey config showserver Description: show the bots servers. Usage: hey showserver
